{"tid":1918087,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"侵侵將會公布重大經濟措施救巿 / 美國傳准中國有條件延購美商品","createTime":"2020-03-10T01:17:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T01:22:58.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b3e13c51f0dc76e5a039a51fcc6a1a856c7af442","tid":1918087,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T01:17:48.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普表示，將會宣布嚴厲措施，以減輕新型肺炎疫情在美國蔓延的經濟影響。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普說，當地星期二下午會在白宮舉行記者會，屆時會公布重大的經濟措施。他將會與國會討論，下調或減免薪資稅，又會討論為領取時薪的工人提供幫助。<br />\n<br />\n財長努欽就表示，美國將動用所有工具應對疫情對經濟的影響。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1513454-20200310.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1513454-20200310.htm&d=m5cPLj0qQ3YL0oTVN36eSvlfYAHTsiVLqq1%2Bkbj60LM%3D&h=7b928ea2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1513454-20200310.htm&h=ae688c6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1513454-20200310.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n白宮傳准中國有條件延購美商品<br />\n<br />\n受新冠肺炎疫情影響，外界關注中國如何兌現與美國貿易協議中的購買承諾協議。彭博引述華盛頓和北京方面的知情人士稱，由於北京正致力控制疫情，拖累對美國進口商品的需求，白宮官員已告知中方，願意就中國加大進口美國商品的承諾展現一定的靈活性，前提是中國要確保全面復工後的出口不會飆升，導致中美之間的貿易失衡擴大。 ...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2398624/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2398624%2F&d=m5cPLj0qQ3YL0oTVN36eSvlfYAHTsiVLqq1%2Bkbj60LM%3D&h=094d7221\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2398624/</a>"},{"pid":"da67f932cecd562a686bd8b83c24ecf942a04219","tid":1918087,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T01:18:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0505d56689e42f6581a9f1bb4a4ebe25f00b200","tid":1918087,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T01:22:58.000Z","msg":"前提是中國要確保全面復工後的出口不會飆升，導致中美之間的貿易失衡擴大。<br />\n<br />\n等支那唔好一方面扮死狗<br />\n一方面又瘋狂出口賺外匯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}